## Criteria selection ##
### Detect & set flag ###
1. ✓Add model to store flag
    * ✓Name - slug
    * ✓Active - bool
    * ✓Priority - int
    * ✓Conflicts - m2m to self
2. ✓Add model to store criteria
    * ✓Name - slug
    * ✓Persistent - bool
    * ✓Flags - m2m to flag
    * ✓Everyone - choice (unknown, yes, no)
    * ✓Testing - bool
    * ✓Users - m2m to users
    * ✓Groups - m2m to groups
    * ✓Percent - float (0.0-99.9)
    * ✓Superusers - bool
    * ✓Staff - bool
    * ✓Authenticated - bool
    * ✓Referrer - text (comma seperated)
    * ✓Entry url - text (comma seperated)
    * ✓Device - choice (mobile, tablet, desktop)
    * ✓Query Args - json field
    * ✓Notes - text
    * ✓Languages? - text (comma seperated)
    * ✓Max Cookie age? - int (seconds)
    * ✗Actions taken? - ?
3. Add middleware to detect
    * ✓Looks at incoming requests
    * Caches flag if not cached
    * ✓Finds criteria matches, first in conflict priority wins
    * Add flag to request
    * Add cookie to indicate flags if persistant
4. Check for flag from view and/or template
5. Goal tracking
    * Persona Custom variable
    * Event log
    * GA social share

